quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  111,1,"A Abʋʋ Lahab nus a yiibã halkame, a pʋs n halkame."
  111,2,"A arzεk ning a sẽn mikã pa naf-a, a sẽn n tʋm n paam me (ka naf-a ye)."
  111,3,"B na n yõog-a-la bugum sẽn tar zεlma."
  111,4,"La a pagã sẽn ya ra-tʋkdã(n lobd gõosã Nɑbiyɑɑmã sorẽ)."
  111,5,"Tɩ b ning a yublẽ wã, tãoon-kεgems wĩiri, (n tɑt-ɑ n reed bugmẽ wã)."
